Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.08,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an7\1c&H1D2D24&\fs30\bord0\fsp0\fax-0.1\frz343.4\pos(991.5,603.5)}我們馬上就要去修學旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.08,Text-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\an7\1c&H1D2D24&\fs30\bord0\fsp0\fax-0.1\frz343.4\pos(950.8,962.8)}不送我巧克力嗎？
